    "title": "Junior Frontend Developer at Microsoft India",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Frontend Developer looking for your next big career move? Microsoft India in Ghaziabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Microsoft India:\nMicrosoft India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Rust\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Microsoft India!",
